message.body: Hey, do you know anyone selling a late 90s early 2000s VW TDI? Preferably for under $3k?
Yeah right!!!!! Tdi's are bringing huge money what ur looking for generally brings 5-7k minimum
When is it? Craigslist is full of scams
Hmmm... Kathy had said she saw something around my mark on Craigslist. Lemme call her. Goin to Elf's BBQ?
This Saturday. You got a Facebook invite.
My bad, Kathy was looking at a gas Jetta, $1500
The TDI she saw was 3.5
K
I need a commuter car. Got a new job.
Don't u have a Prius?
Yeah, but we only have one car. Kathy has been driving me to the airport on Monday morning, I fly somewhere, rent a car, and then she picks me up Thursday night or Friday morning.
That's what I thought u were doing so now u want another fuel friendly car?
New job is in Conshohocken and being driven to work and picked up each day isn't goin to work out that well.
I'll keep an eye out
Thanks! Of course if that TR6 with the Wankel is still kicking around, I'd consider it...
Where's elf live these days
Northwest Philadelphia. Haven't been there t yet, just looked it up on Google maps.
Dude, we just passed you on Macdade when you were merging off of 476
No, I'm still in bed
Oh... Well you've got a look alike driving a crown Vic.
Damn look a likes
Yeah!
